<lyrics>[V1]
. Em             C       D
 Kıeli Táńir, umtylam Saǵan
.       Am        B7      Em
 Jan tynyshtyǵy Sende, bilemin.

[C1]
.         Am            Em
   // Keýdeńde Seniń tabamyn tynym,
.     Am      B7     Em
   Basylady júregim meniń //

[V2]
 Bilemin Sende máńgi qýanysh
 Jáne baıandy mahabbat.

[V3]
 Eshkim meni endi aıyra almaıdy,
 Bul máńgilik qýanyshtan.

[V4]
 Kelgende meniń aqyrǵy demim,
 Qabyldarsyń meni, senemin.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
<title>Kıeli Táńir, umtylam Saǵan РӘЖ3 ҮРәж89</title>
